OL,3,CThe new service that's helping cancer
OL,4,Cpatients and reducing A&E pressures
OL,6,FA new specialised same-day service
OL,7,Fhelping cancer patients who develop
OL,8,Fadverse side effects as a result of
OL,9,Ftheir treatment, is also reducing
OL,10,Fpressures on A&E departments.
OL,12,FThe service, launched at in Cardiff,
OL,13,Fprovides early detection of immune-
OL,14,Frelated reactions, also known as
OL,15,F'toxicities'. It means these side
OL,16,Feffects can be treated sooner.
OL,18,FIt also helps patients avoid repeated
OL,19,Fadmissions to the emergency department.
