OL,3,CThe new service that's helping cancer
OL,4,Cpatients and reducing A&E pressures
OL,6,FSharon Bettinson from Caerphilly is
OL,7,Fcurrently undergoing immunotherapy at
OL,8,FVelindre. She said the side effects
OL,9,Ffrom her cancer is causing a greater
OL,10,Fimpact than the cancer itself.
OL,12,F"Ten days after I started getting the
OL,13,Feffects. I had a rash, a severe rash
OL,14,Fall over my body", she explained.
OL,16,F"I had swollen eyes, I to have a
OL,17,Fpacemaker fitted because I had a heart
OL,18,Fblock and a clot on my lung."
