OL,3,CThe new service that's helping cancer
OL,4,Cpatients and reducing A&E pressures
OL,6,FHowever, it comes with a range of side
OL,7,Feffects as the revved up immune system
OL,8,Fcan also fight the body's healthy
OL,9,Fcells.
OL,11,FDr Jo Ocen, Consultant Oncologist,
OL,12,Fexplains: "These side effects can be
OL,13,Fimmune related so basically
OL,14,Finflammation that can affect different
OL,15,Fparts of the body essentially, and
OL,16,Fsometimes these side effects can be
OL,17,Fvery serious."
