OL,3,CThe new service that's helping cancer
OL,4,Cpatients and reducing A&E pressures
OL,6,FThe project is aimed at improving the
OL,7,Fexperience of patients receiving
OL,8,Fcancer treatment, as well as reducing
OL,9,Fthe pressure general emergency
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FThis new service has led to 200,000
OL,13,Fpeople in Wales in 2023 getting urgent
OL,14,Femergency treatment in the right place
OL,15,Fthe first time.
