OL,3,CThe new service that's helping cancer
OL,4,Cpatients and reducing A&E pressures
OL,6,FBut it is hoped the #25 million Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment initiative will help
OL,8,Fstabilise A&E waiting times and
OL,9,Fambulance handover times.
OL,11,FHayley Mian, Specialist Nurse, said:
OL,12,F"Those are patients that would have
OL,13,Fpresented to an A&E department in
OL,14,Fcrisis and would potentially have had
OL,15,Fa very different outcome if they
OL,16,Fhadn't been mopped up by our service."
